    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_Start">Start the Go service in WSL (run-server.sh); /api/health wait time is configured in Settings — Wait &amp; health tab.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_Stop">Stop the docklite-wsl process (scripts/stop-server.sh).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_Restart">Restart the service (scripts/restart-server.sh); /api/health wait time is configured in Settings — Wait &amp; health tab.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_Help" xml:space="preserve">Feature overview and tips for the current page. Press F5 to refresh the current page (except Settings and Cleanup).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_Bar" xml:space="preserve">Status line: /api/health response and service version in WSL. Start / Stop / Restart control the docklite-wsl process. F5 refreshes the current page (Dashboard, Containers, Logs, …).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Header_ProgressBar">Progress while waiting for the service after app launch or after Start/Restart (timeouts are in Settings).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Ui_Tooltip_Sidebar_Nav" xml:space="preserve">Switch pages quickly. F5 refreshes the current page (except Settings and Cleanup).</sys:String>

